          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>21st Century Investment Act of 201</strong><b>9</b></p> <p>This bill modifies the tax credit for increasing research activities to allow an increased 25% tax credit rate for amounts paid or incurred to any person (other than an employee of the taxpayer) for research, substantially all of which occurs in the United States.</p>]]></text>
